posts.post_title: WTB - T206 Complete (Near Complete) Set or Bulk
posts.post_content:
I would like to own a complete T206 set.  Ideally, I would like to acquire an entire graded set, preferably PSA but would consider SGC, and preferably in Mid-Grade (3-6).  

I would also buy larger graded collections and assemble myself, as I already own the Big 4 and all of the big HOFers.  

Please email or PM me if you have something to sell.

Ryan

Go get em' Ryan.

Good luck!
I'll just go ahead and knock out the Big 4 real quick first; then fill in the tough ones later..HA!!

Good luck Ryan, you obviously have the big boys out of the way.

If I were you, I'd keep a saved eBay search for "T206 Lot", and you'll occasionally see some decent lots, often graded.
